title: Hummus House UK
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Take away falafel wrap stall has a choice of vegan items such as chickpea falafel balls hummus, tahini, freshly chopped tomatoes, lettuce, cucumber, pickled gherkins, pickled parsnip. A small separate area is dedicated for their meat products, which do not contaminate the vegan area.
